You're the evidence.

301
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:52,600
Me?

302
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:55,160
Come on.

303
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,280
If she really is the one behind the attack,

304
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:58,480
she'll kill me!

305
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,720
Why would I report her? I don't want to die.

306
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,360
Besides,

307
00:13:01,660 --> 00:13:03,080
I came to you for another business

308
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,640
more important than this.

309
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,170
Let's go.

310
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:04,960
What?

311
00:13:05,880 --> 00:13:07,120
You'd better behave yourself,

312
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,280
or I'll report to Director Guo.

313
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,280
Don't drag me.

314
00:13:09,660 --> 00:13:10,800
Where are you taking me?

315
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:12,060
You don't need to know.

316
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:12,920
Stop it.

317
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,640
You've crossed the line.

318
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:15,980
Qu Manting.

319
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,320
How could you do this?

320
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,440
Shut up.

321
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,620
Don't you know me well enough?

322
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,040
I need a favor.

323
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:27,440
What is it?

324
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:51,440
Why did you bring me here?

325
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:54,480
It's for your good.

326
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:55,930
What do you mean?

327
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,760
I've prepared a gift for you.

328
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:01,000
Half of the young ladies in Shunyuan

329
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,530
are all at this racecourse.

330
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:05,440
Tell me if there's anyone you like.

331
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,680
I'll fix you two up.

332
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,560
Are you a matchmaker now?

333
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,440
I'm trying to help.

334
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,540
Those escorts I introduced you

335
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:13,240
aren't your type.

336
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,200
Okay, fine.

337
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,460
I know your bar is high.

338
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,320
Ladies here are different.

339
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,760
They're all good-looking

340
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:19,840
and from prominent families.

341
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,900
Any one of them is good enough for you.

342
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:23,360
Should I thank you?

343
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,120
You're welcome.

344
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:26,320
You just won't let Gu Yanzhen go, right?

345
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:27,360
Ms. Qu,

346
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,290
please let me go.

347
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,800
You can go talk to Gu Yanzhen.

348
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:31,120
Why are you torturing me?

349
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:31,800
I don't care.

350
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:33,520
Only when you find your Miss.right

351
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:34,650
can I feel relieved.

352
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,480
I can't pick a random one.

353
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,880
You have nothing to worry about.

354
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:39,280
I can introduce them to you.

355
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,400
I don't know them.

356
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,800
You will after you see them.

357
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:42,800
I don't like them.

358
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,860
Affection can be cultivated.

359
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,050
Listen to me,

360
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,800
your sergeant assigned you to me.

361
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:49,130
Before we get this done,

362
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,240
you won't be able to go back.

363
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,120
You're evil!

364
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,780
Come, let's go have a look.

365
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:16,880
Manting.

366
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,520
What do you think, Qianqian?

367
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:27,320
Looking good?

368
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,420
Not too bad.

369
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:29,450
You're late.

370
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,040
Let me introduce.

371
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:31,760
This is my friend

372
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:32,620
Zhao Qianqian.

373
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:33,480
Hello.

374
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,040
What's going on?

375
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,680
Move! Step aside!

376
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:42,320
Qiqi.

377
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,080
Get out of the way.

378
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:48,760
Move.

379
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,080
Are you OK?

380
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:05,610
Are you alright?

381
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:06,360
Are you OK?

382
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:08,440
It's scary.

383
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:10,690
Let's go.

384
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:12,250
We can have a rest there.

385
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:12,920
Don't ride the horse.

386
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:13,450
Let's go.

387
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:15,650
Let's go.

388
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:19,800
What's wrong with you?

389
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:21,460
Didn't you say you could ride?

390
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:23,600
I could.

391
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,840
Only a little bit.

392
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:25,360
You...

393
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:28,160
When I was little, I rode the horse in my dad's arms.

394
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:30,520
Hadn't it been for him,

395
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:32,240
you would've been dead, you know?

396
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,640
If anything bad happened to you,

397
00:16:33,640 --> 00:16:35,080
what should I say to your parents?

398
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,040
Enough, Qianqian.

399
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:36,800
Calm down.

400
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,450
Everything is fine now.

401
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,560
Why don't you introduce us?

402
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:42,080
I've never met her before.

403
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:44,090
This is Qiqi, my cousin.

404
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,240
And this is

405
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,080
Qu Manting.

406
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:49,120
Weren't you eager to see her?

407
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:50,760
Ms. Qu,

408
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,010
nice to meet you.

409
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:53,000
You know me?

410
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,200
I've heard your songs.

411
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:56,400
Perhaps,

412
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:58,500
we may be relatives in the future.

413
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:00,840
You're my alleged sister-in-law.

414
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:02,440
Alleged sister-in-law?

415
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,560
Who's your brother?

416
00:17:05,829 --> 00:17:06,440
She's

417
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:08,109
Gu Yanzhen's sister.

418
00:17:10,589 --> 00:17:11,560
His sister?

419
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,369
The one and only?

420
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:16,740
Come here, you. Come here.

421
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:19,440
So you're my sister, too.

422
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:20,349
Sister.

423
00:17:20,349 --> 00:17:21,720
Sister is too formal.

424
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:22,829
Just call me Manting.

425
00:17:22,829 --> 00:17:23,440
Manting.

426
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,760
Can you two behave like ladies?

427
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:27,400
Oh, come on.

428
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,460
We're just joking.

429
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:30,600
Who is this?

430
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,450
Thanks for your help today.

431
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:34,280
It's nothing.

432
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:35,560
It's not.

433
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:36,680
We all saw it.

434
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:37,760
That horse ran wild

435
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:38,720
and charged towards us.

436
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:39,340
Without you,

437
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:40,160
she'd be dead.

438
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:41,400
Come.

439
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,940
Let me introduce you guys.

440
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:44,240
This is

441
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:46,340
a straight-A student at the Arsenal Military Academy,

442
00:17:46,340 --> 00:17:47,400
also my good friend

443
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:49,960
from Peking, Xie Liangchen.

444
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,720
Come and say hi.

445
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,600
He's a soldier.

446
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:56,800
Qiqi,

447
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,480
say thank you to Mr. Xie

448
00:17:58,720 --> 00:17:59,920
for saving your life.

449
00:18:00,340 --> 00:18:01,080
No need.

450
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:03,280
-What are you waiting for? -Have we met before?

451
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:04,440
Come and thank Mr. Xie.

452
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,700
Why aren't you moving?

453
00:18:12,100 --> 00:18:13,030
Are you alright?

454
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:14,440
Is he dead?

455
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:15,800
It's none of your business.

456
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:16,400
Leave now!

457
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,720
What should we do?

458
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:19,400
Not your concern.

459
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,080
Run!

460
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:21,720
I know!

461
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,640
You know nothing about

462
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,000
what happened to Shen Junshan that night,

463
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,130
and you saw nothing.

464
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:29,100
Don't go for him again

465
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:30,200
and don't tell anyone about it.

466
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:30,720
Got it?

467
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:36,170
You know each other?

468
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,600
We don't!

469
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:43,050
Then why are you so excited?

470
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:46,120
I mean...

471
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:49,280
I mean it reminds of the Arsenal Military Academy.

472
00:18:49,280 --> 00:18:51,210
My brother is also a student there.

473
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:52,540
Xie Liangchen, right?

474
00:18:52,560 --> 00:18:53,560
My name is Gu Qiqi.

475
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:54,280
Hello.

476
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,240
Hi.

477
00:19:10,560 --> 00:19:11,420
Eat the kebabs.

478
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:21,180
I remember you.

479
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:23,880
Don't worry.

480
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,010
I won't tell anyone.

481
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:27,480
Last time, at school,

482
00:19:27,760 --> 00:19:28,800
you saved me once,

483
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:31,040
and you saved me again today.

484
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:33,880
I owe you two lives already.

485
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:36,080
Hey,

486
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:38,560
remember that man you hit with a rock?

487
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:39,320
Is he dead?

488
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:39,840
Hush.

489
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:43,720
Don't worry,

490
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:44,920
others can't hear us.

491
00:19:45,240 --> 00:19:46,400
Tell me, is he dead?

492
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:47,720
No.

493
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,400
How come?

494
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:53,320
How did he survive after such a heavy blow?

495
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,640
He's quite lucky.

496
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:56,080
You wish him dead?

497
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,680
Of course. He's a bad guy.

498
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:01,440
For a little girl like you,

499
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:03,040
you sure are cruel-hearted.

500
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:04,280
I'm not little.

501
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:05,680
I'm 16 years old.

502
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:07,960
I can get married in the village.

503
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:13,400
Miss Zhao, can you roast it?

504
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,440
I can.

505
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:15,880
You can do it yourself.

506
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:17,960
I don't want to be near the smoke.

507
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:22,840
I heard from Qu Manting

508
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:25,320
that you came to find a date.

509
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,660
Do you have anyone in mind?

510
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:35,200
What do you think of me?

511
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:45,040
I know I like you.

512
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:47,730
I think we're destined to meet each other.

513
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,920
Last year, my mom hired a fortuneteller

514
00:20:51,080 --> 00:20:53,760
who said I'd bring good fortune to my future husband.

515
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:56,220
Whoever marries me will be the luckiest man.

516
00:20:57,760 --> 00:20:59,890
No wonder you're Gu Yanzhen's sister.

517
00:21:01,040 --> 00:21:01,920
Of course.

518
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:06,560
Ms. Qu,

519
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:07,680
here.

520
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:08,600
Thanks.

521
00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:12,960
Goodness!

522
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,520
I'll get fat after eating this.

523
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:15,380
You can have it.

524
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:19,800
Believe it or not,

525
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,300
I'm telling the truth.

526
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:22,880
You know,

527
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:25,340
that fortuneteller has never been wrong.

528
00:21:25,340 --> 00:21:27,200
Last year, he said that my brother

529
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,880
would get into trouble at the beginning of the year.

530
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:31,810
Then before the first month ended,

531
00:21:32,100 --> 00:21:34,400
he was beaten by my father

532
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:36,040
and almost died.

533
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,930
Did your dad beat him often?

534
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:39,640
He did,

535
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:40,650
but not anymore.

536
00:21:41,280 --> 00:21:44,000
The thing is my brother dares to fight back now

537
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:45,140
and he can run fast.

538
00:21:53,320 --> 00:21:53,920
Qianqian,

539
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,600
why didn't you tell me

540
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:58,160
you were related to the Gus?

541
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,010
We aren't too close.

542
00:22:01,340 --> 00:22:01,880
Besides,

543
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:04,860
are you really in love with my cousin?

544
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:05,920
Of course I am.

545
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,700
Then, I wish you good luck.

546
00:22:09,320 --> 00:22:12,080
My cousin isn't an ordinary man.

547
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:14,800
I know.

548
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:16,760
That's what I like about him.

549
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:20,600
I've spent some time

550
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:21,930
with the fortuneteller

551
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:23,560
and learned a few things.

552
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:25,410
Do you want me to read your palm?

553
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,160
Forget it.

554
00:22:37,080 --> 00:22:38,080
I see.

555
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:40,560
You're doomed

556
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,720
to have tons of wooers this year.

557
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,760
You can tell that from the back of my hand?

558
00:22:45,760 --> 00:22:46,440
Of course.

559
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:48,620
I'm good at reading the back, too.

560
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:51,400
How about you take your clothes off and let me see?

561
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:52,860
Don't even think about it.

562
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,330
You're quite talented.

563
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,060
Just so-so.

564
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:19,210
Get down.

565
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:20,960
Go.

566
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:24,320
Qianqian,

567
00:23:24,320 --> 00:23:24,920
come here.

568
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,200
Get down.

569
00:23:34,760 --> 00:23:35,360
Come here.

570
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:40,360
Qiqi.

571
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:41,300
Liangchen.

572
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:50,970
Let's go.

573
00:24:03,320 --> 00:24:04,380
I've seen that man.

574
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,760
He works for Jin Xianrong.

575
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:08,220
A few days ago, he tried to kill Shen Junshan.

576
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:11,520
What should we do now?

577
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,940
Go back to the Academy.

578
00:24:24,040 --> 00:24:25,040
Don't be upset.

579
00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:26,840
This place is fun.

580
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:28,490
Let's go play together.

581
00:24:28,760 --> 00:24:29,600
Come on.

582
00:24:44,600 --> 00:24:45,160
Junshan,

583
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:48,000
I have something to tell you.

584
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:49,040
What's up?

585
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:50,930
Come with me.

586
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,570
You're leaving?

587
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:56,040
Fine, fine, fine.

588
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,280
We can go together.

589
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,960
He left to date.

590
00:25:01,100 --> 00:25:01,920
Not enough people.

591
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:02,440
Forget it.

592
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:03,600
I'm begging you.

593
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,440
Please go with you.

594
