889
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:50,530
Don't worry.

890
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:51,810
I'll take care of it.

891
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,530
Let me take you back.

892
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:56,760
No need.

893
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:57,920
I can go back myself.

894
00:40:57,920 --> 00:40:59,120
How will you go back?

895
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:02,040
Let me give you a ride. My car is outside.

896
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:03,520
OK.

897
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:05,200
I'm leaving then.

898
00:41:06,700 --> 00:41:07,440
Take care.

899
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,400
Let's go, Xie Liangchen.

900
00:41:13,120 --> 00:41:14,040
You go ahead.

901
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:14,800
I'm fine.

902
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:19,160
Leave with Manting.

903
00:41:20,160 --> 00:41:22,290
I'll have someone take her back later.

904
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:23,680
Thank you.

905
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,560
Be careful.

906
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,240
You too.

907
00:41:29,640 --> 00:41:30,560
You saw what happened.

908
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:31,690
Stay out of trouble.

909
00:41:32,560 --> 00:41:33,160
I will.

910
00:41:36,840 --> 00:41:37,480
Liu,

911
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:40,160
you take Xiaojun back.

912
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:40,840
OK.

913
00:41:41,400 --> 00:41:41,930
Let's go.

914
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:42,880
Sister,

915
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:43,610
I'm leaving.

916
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,120
Boss,

917
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:00,800
we caught him.

918
00:42:02,160 --> 00:42:03,020
What did he say?

919
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:04,970
He said nothing.

920
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,460
He killed himself.

921
00:42:08,700 --> 00:42:09,700
Where's the body?

922
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:11,260
In the west warehouse.

923
00:42:14,700 --> 00:42:15,320
Boss.

924
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:22,980
Take off his pants.

925
00:42:30,640 --> 00:42:31,200
Boss,

926
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,140
he's Japanese.

927
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:36,000
Dump him outside the Japanese Chamber.

928
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,400
Got it.

929
00:43:07,320 --> 00:43:08,520
Telegraph Watanabe.

930
00:43:08,560 --> 00:43:10,280
Tell him to leave for Liaoxi immediately.

931
00:43:10,280 --> 00:43:11,840
I need him at the auction.

932
00:43:11,840 --> 00:43:12,440
Boss,

933
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:15,650
please give me another chance.

934
00:43:22,700 --> 00:43:24,520
Do you deserve a second chance?

935
00:43:24,760 --> 00:43:25,880
If I fail again,

936
00:43:26,800 --> 00:43:28,320
I'll kill myself.

937
00:43:30,320 --> 00:43:30,840
Boss,

938
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:31,840
Lord Chengrui is outside

939
00:43:31,840 --> 00:43:32,840
asking to see you.

940
00:43:38,720 --> 00:43:40,160
This is your last chance.
